Centenarian shares secrets of long life

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 102-year-old County Antrim man has been sharing his secrets on how to live a long life.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
25 November 2016 Last updated at 07:12 GMT
John McLarnon is one of a number of older people talking part in a BBC NI appeal on behalf of Age NI.
Playing Our Part looks at the contribution made by older people.
